             was indicted for <rs id="t18120916-37-off205" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18120916-37-off205" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18120916-37-off205" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18120916-37-cd206" type="crimeDate">25th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120916-37-off205 t18120916-37-cd206"></join>, fifteen yards of silk, value 4 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18120916-37-victim356" type="victimName">
                           Robert Andrews 
                           Clarke
                        <interp inst="t18120916-37-victim356" type="surname" value="Clarke"></interp>
