               GUILTY
            </rs>, <rs id="t18120916-37-punish210" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18120916-37-punish210" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120916-37-defend354 t18120916-37-punish210"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 23.</p>
               <p>London Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
